title: For Sale/Trade:  Norinco AK-47
postcontent: Excellent condition Norinco 56S Transitional AK47. One of the best examples I have seen, as close to a pre ban Chinese rifle as you can get without being an actual pre ban. This was caught in customs at the time the 1989 Ban went into effect. At the first of the ban there was not a proper way of debanning and different importers did different things. This one does not have Mak90, SP or Sporter electo penned or stamped, the only things that makes this not a pre ban is a number of importers were struck out as some importers didn't want to deal with the ban and the bayonet lugs have been ground off. This rifle was originally meant to have a Chinese Type 2 bayonet, but the fangs were left remaining and a Chinese Type 1 bayonet will lock up tight. Original Chinese furniture and the bluing is excellent, no rust or pitting. A very, very nice rifle. Call or text 918 371 six250.
